	            <h5>Featured</h5>
            <hr />
          <h4>How to Connect your MT3809 with FOUNDATION™ Fieldbus Transmitter to the Network</h4>

<p>The Brooks Instrument MT3809 metal tube variable area flow meter is now available with an optional FOUNDATION™ Fieldbus transmitter. The addition of the FOUNDATION™ Fieldbus transmitter makes it easier to integrate the popular MT3809 with automation control systems across the plant enterprise. 
<br /><br />
Follow our step-by-step video to learn how to connect the meter to your FOUNDATION™ Fieldbus network.</p>

<iframe width="375" height="210" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/KOgdtYaxHjc" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen></iframe>
